			</div>
			<div class="testimonial-card">
				<p>"I had multiple electrical issues that other companies couldn't solve. Handyman Hinchman identified and fixed everything in one visit!"</p>
				<p class="customer-name">- Michael R.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="contact-cta">
		<h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
		<p>Contact us today for a free quote on your project</p>
		<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Us</a>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.hero {
		background-color: var(--primary-color);
		color: white;
		padding: 4rem 1rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.hero-content {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.hero h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.hero p {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.cta-buttons {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 1rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.btn {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 4px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: bold;
		transition: background-color 0.3s;
	}

	.btn-primary {
		background-color: var(--accent-color);
		color: var(--text-color);
	}

	.btn-primary:hover {
		background-color: #e69009;
	}

	.btn-secondary {
		background-color: white;
		color: var(--primary-color);
	}

	.btn-secondary:hover {
		background-color: #f3f4f6;
	}

	section {
		margin: 4rem 0;
	}

	h2 {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		color: var(--primary-color);
	}

	.services-grid, .testimonial-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.service-card {
		background-color: #f9fafb;
		border-radius: 8px;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		text-align: center;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		transition: transform 0.3s;
	}

	.service-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
	}

	.service-icon {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.services-link {
		text-align: center;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	.services-link a {
		color: var(--primary-color);
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	.services-link a:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	.about-preview {
		background-color: #f3f4f6;
		padding: 3rem 1rem;
	}

	.about-content {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.benefits-list {
		margin: 2rem 0;
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
	}

	.benefits-list li {
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.learn-more {
		display: inline-block;
		color: var(--primary-color);
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	.learn-more:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	.testimonial-card {
		background-color: white;
		border-radius: 8px;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}

	.customer-name {
		font-weight: bold;
		text-align: right;
		color: var(--secondary-color);
	}

	.contact-cta {
		text-align: center;
		background-color: var(--primary-color);
		color: white;
		padding: 3rem 1rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 4rem auto;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hero h1 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.hero p {
			font-size: 1.2rem;
		}

		.services-grid, .testimonial-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
